STEP 2:  Load The Logos 

1.   Click Insert from the panel.

2.    Select Image Option.

3.   Look for your file.

4.   Select Visa Logo.



   5. Repeat the same process to upload the Colaberry Logo. 
   6. Display both logos on the side of the Title as shown below.

              Visa Logo:   X Position:0     Y Position:1     Width:129      Height:70

              Colaberry Logo:  X position: 1169     Y Position:0    Width: 129     Height:70

   7. Select both logos and click "Bring Forward"
